action_extraction.template:
Extract all action items, tasks, and deadlines from this email.

Email:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Respond with ONLY a valid JSON object (no other text). Use this exact structure:
{{"tasks": [{{"task": "task description", "deadline": "date or null", "priority": "high/medium/low"}}]}}

auto_reply.template:
